task.summary: Added configuration support (e.g., RabbitMQ server address); added SMP support to vm.args; modified relx.config to include required applications for Erlang Observer.
Added Makefile support for "rebar get-deps". Tried adding Inaka's worker_pool to support publishing, but ended up pulling it out.
Added support from a single publishing process to a pool of publishing processes, each with their own RabbitMQ connection and channel.
